#~ msgstr "Fai clic con il &LMB; su un collegamento in una pagina per aprirlo."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To open a link in a new instance of &konqueror;, leaving the old page "
#~ "still visible, &RMB; click on the link and select the <guimenuitem>Open "
#~ "in New Window</guimenuitem> option. Alternatively, you might want to "
#~ "<guimenuitem>Open in New Tab</guimenuitem>. <link linkend=\"tabbrowse"
